<reply id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/1999-10-20.16.r0" speakerid="uk.org.publicwhip/member/80134" speakername="Sarah Boyack" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-99/wa1020.htm#1667">

  <p>The contract between Scottish Ministers and Skye Bridge Ltd requires the company to remove the toll collection facilities at the end of the concession period. Toll collection facilities are defined in section 39(4) of the New Roads and Street Works Act 1991.</p>

</reply>


